metadata.name: FreeFall
metadata.description:
Freefall Event Poster Edition ! 

We wanted to offer something affordable for people that want to support our artistic cause and be a part of this event. 
All the proceeds from sale go to The Giving Block "Impact Index Fund: Mental Health" . FND by automation makes the  creator take 1% but those and any other possible percentages will also be manually donated post drop. 

Poster created by Boxhead and The Hiena
